务员录用考试‘35 周岁以下’的限制。」这将有利于对全社会就业或者再就业起到示范性作用，有助于解决就业市场上的年龄歧视。上热搜！委员建议放宽 35 岁就业年龄限制"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-416629ea8bce956314c73b2a82572a67_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "48 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/647102957"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IooWajuv2hN4WEAMaCTEwNjA3ODAxMCC2yJmvBjAAOHhABXIJNjQ3MTAyOTU3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1709648221.939892", "card_id": "Q_647123156", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 39}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待 Yuzu 模拟器和任天堂达成庭外和解，前者赔偿任天堂 240 万美元并停运业务？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "任天堂与柚子模拟器达成庭外和解：后者赔偿 240 万美元 停运业务"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-b0c0477bb09acdcdd8f3c3d5997f3759_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "45 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/647123156"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIooWajuv2hN4WEAMaCTEwNjA4MjUyMyDVlJqvBjAAOIABQAZyCTY0NzEyMzE1NngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1709648221.940941", "card_id": "Q_644483736", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 19}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《灌篮高手》如若各队拿掉各位王牌，哪队的综合实力最强?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-f894cb2b731399e119f7e1eba0239760_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "45 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link